{"id":645,"date":"2024-08-02T19:58:19","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T19:58:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=645"},"modified":"2024-08-02T19:58:19","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T19:58:19","slug":"tm038-fire-blast","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm038-fire-blast\/","title":{"rendered":"TM038 Fire Blast"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM038 Fire Blast<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>On the ground on the Cinder Volcano 3F\u2019s East side. Requires Rock Climb.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>The foe is hit with an intense flame. It may leave the target with a burn.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>5<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Fire<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Cinder Volcano<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm08-rock-climb\/\">Rock Climb<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Enter Cinder Volcano from the East entrance and head North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-going-north-from-the-cinder-volcano-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"Going North from the Cinder Volcano entrance. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going North from the Cinder Volcano entrance.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Climb up the first ladder you see.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-ladder-up-to-the-2nd-floor.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the ladder up to the second floor. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the ladder up to the second floor.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From here, follow the path up the long set of stairs and continue West.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-up-the-west-stairs.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path up the West stairs. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path up the West stairs.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the ladder next to the mountain climber NPC to go further up.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-ladder-up-to-the-3rd-floor.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the ladder up to the third floor. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the ladder up to the third floor.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After reaching the third floor, follow the path East and then North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-following-the-only-available-path.jpg\" alt=\"Following the only available path. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the only available path.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue going North and take the ladder to the fourth floor.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-ladder-to-the-4th-floor.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the ladder to the fourth floor. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the ladder to the fourth floor.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>On the fourth floor, continue following the only available path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-following-the-only-available-path.jpg\" alt=\"Following the only available path. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the only available path.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll come to a crossroad where the path will split North and West. Take the path North where you\u2019ll find a ladder bringing you down to the third floor again.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/08-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-ladder-to-go-down-to-the-3rd-floor.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the ladder to go down to the third floor. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the ladder to go down to the third floor.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From here, walk West past a bridge to see the TM for Fire Blast in a lower section of the cave. It\u2019s obtainable by using Rock Climb to scale the wall.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/09-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-tm-for-fire-blast.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the TM for Fire Blast. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the TM for Fire Blast.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":646,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-645","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-js